  "texts": [
    "Given the growing volume of literature on AI applications in telecom, the quality of selected articles was evaluated using the PRISMA checklist.",
    "This method ensured that only highquality studies were included in the review.",
    "The PRISMA technique also facilitated the critical assessment of each paper, focusing on the applicability of AI, machine learning algorithms, and novel techniques in anomaly detection for telecom infrastructure.",
    "Figure 5 illustrates the PRISMA process used in this review.",
    "Following a thorough evaluation of 3084 articles gathered from multiple sources (Springer, IEEE, Science Direct, Google Scholar, and arXiv) during the initial stage, 1434 articles were excluded due to duplication across these repositories."
